divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking pictures of planes making "Xs" in the sky. Most conspiracy theorists call these chemtrails. I was not expecting to catch anything. I just aimed at the "X" and lines and shot with my camera. I did not see anything with my naked eye. Upon inspection of the pictures later reveled what looks like a white aspirin circle to the left of the sun with a red-ish hew around it. If I were to take a guess, it is a UFO with some kind of force-field. I also caught some pictures with what looks to be orbs in them, but I am not sure why they would be caught within the same minutes. It could be nothing, but I thought it was worth sharing.
Summary: White circle shape with red dome (looked like a forcefield) to the Left of the sun
